      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking at our quarterly report for the warehouse and we've got a 3% discrepancy between what the system says we have and what's actually on the shelves. What are the standard industry methods for auditing this kind of shrinkage?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
