      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, we've looked at the access logs and everything seems fine on paper, which is what's so frustrating. It's like the items just vanish into thin air. Do you have anything in your experience regarding \"unexplained shrinkage\" that isn't just simple employee theft or bad paperwork? Any other patterns to look for?",
